{"tid":2512640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公主牛一｜夏洛特公主長髮披肩迎6歲生日 皇室攝影師：她越來越像爸爸","createTime":"2021-05-02T01:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T03:44:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"117f66371ba2de6d9f840e4e906575f0cd133e97","tid":2512640,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"英國夏洛特公主周日6歲生日，媽媽凱蒂周六公開她為女兒拍攝的生日照，可見夏洛特已經長髮披肩，皇室攝影師讚她是「美麗女孩」。<br />\n<br />\n新照周末在諾福克郡（Norfolk）的別墅拍攝。皇室攝影師愛德華茲（Arthur Edwards）說夏洛特長得越來越像爸爸威廉王子，而凱蒂的攝影技術亦更上一層樓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210502/NMQZRR5VRRBUVEGFCF2ONHQX4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210502%2FNMQZRR5VRRBUVEGFCF2ONHQX4M%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=6e790ac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210502%2FNMQZRR5VRRBUVEGFCF2ONHQX4M%2F&h=8e8eed76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210502/NMQZRR5VRRBUVEGFCF2ONHQX4M/</a>"},{"pid":"e7a298fc8d4ac4f2f807ce678bb525b251fa4621","tid":2512640,"uid":68215,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"個女似老竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f344a8719aeed4f2e5139721f1d6214e69a66d33","tid":2512640,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e7a298fc8d4ac4f2f807ce678bb525b251fa4621","tid":2512640,"uid":68215,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"個女似老竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf7d524cf6d56e0569439433fa3a79938f8d58e","tid":2512640,"uid":8810,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1